<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="sl">Riverside County Service</p>
    <h2>Riverside County spans from LA exurbs to wine country — each area is different</h2>
    <div class="body-text"><p>Riverside County's western cities — Corona, Murrieta, Temecula, and Menifee — have grown dramatically over the past 15 years. Large suburban housing developments built between 2005 and 2020 mean a significant concentration of Samsung, LG, and GE appliances now entering the 10–15 year repair window. These communities are where repair almost always makes more economic sense than replacement.</p>
        <p>Temecula is different from the rest of the county. The wine country estates around the Temecula Valley run appliances comparable to Newport Beach — Sub-Zero, Wolf, Thermador in the larger properties. The elevation (around 1,500 feet) gives Temecula a slightly cooler climate than the flatland IE cities, but summer afternoons still hit 95°F+.</p>
        <p>Corona and Riverside city face similar heat challenges to San Bernardino County — extreme summer temperatures that stress refrigeration systems. Same day appliance repair in Riverside County is something we've built coverage for specifically in the western cities; for Hemet and eastern communities, we're honest about drive times.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="sl">Service Map</p>
    <h2>Cities we serve in Riverside County</h2>
    <p class="lead">Click any pin for service info, neighborhoods, recent repairs, and local pricing.</p>
  </div>
</section>
