<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="sl">What We Repair</p>
    <h2>Every major home appliance across Riverside County</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <a href="/services/refrigerator-repair-los-angeles/" class="svc-card"><div class="svc-icon">❄️</div><h3>Refrigerator Repair</h3><p>All brands, all types. $200–$450 typical. Sub-Zero and luxury brands serviced.</p></a>
      <a href="/services/washing-machine-repair-los-angeles/" class="svc-card"><div class="svc-icon">👕</div><h3>Washer Repair</h3><p>Front-load, top-load, stacked. $150–$350 typical.</p></a>
      <a href="/services/dryer-repair-los-angeles/" class="svc-card"><div class="svc-icon">💨</div><h3>Dryer Repair</h3><p>Gas and electric. Dryer vent inspection included when relevant.</p></a>
      <a href="/services/dishwasher-repair-los-angeles/" class="svc-card"><div class="svc-icon">🍽️</div><h3>Dishwasher Repair</h3><p>All brands. Miele, Bosch, KitchenAid, Samsung. $150–$320.</p></a>
      <a href="/services/oven-repair-los-angeles/" class="svc-card"><div class="svc-icon">🔥</div><h3>Oven & Range Repair</h3><p>Gas, electric, induction. All brands. $175–$420.</p></a>
      <a href="/services/cooktop-repair-los-angeles/" class="svc-card"><div class="svc-icon">🍳</div><h3>Cooktop Repair</h3><p>Gas, electric, induction. All brands including luxury.</p></a>
