    <div class="faq-list">
      
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Do you offer same day appliance repair across Riverside County?</div><div class="faq-a">Yes. We cover 8 cities across Riverside County. Call (951) 577-3877 for availability in your city.</div></div>
