      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What warranty do you provide on appliance repairs in Riverside County?</div><div class="faq-a">90 days on parts and labor. OEM parts used wherever available. We use your manufacturer warranty rather than voiding it.</div></div>
    
